name: Flags of Osea and Cascadia
description: Flags of fictional nations Osea (above) and Cascadia (below), the former from the Ace Combat universe, and the latter is from Project Wingman's universe. Altough r/acecombat is private in protest of the recent API changes. This didn't seem to stop r/Project_Wingman from making the Osean flag anyways, with both games having overlapping fanbases
